description.en: Agricultural Trade Chain originates from Australia. Through the block chain technology progress, food tracking, traceability and safety are enhanced to protect the value of quality commodities, as well as the product circulation channels and the rights and interests of consumers. In particular, agricultural trade is integrated with supply chains, which are transparent, more effective in ensuring consumer food safety, and provide solutions to the standards and innovations required by the global agricultural trade security ecosystem.
